      "seed": 130321812,
      "version": 272,
      "versionNonce": 1423815898,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479415,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "parent (cancelCtx/timerCtx)\n   ↓ (children 链表)\n   ├─ child1 (cancelCtx)\n   │     ↓\n   │     └─ grandchild1\n   └─ child2 (timerCtx)\n父取消 → 所有子、孙全部级联取消\n子取消 → 不影响父和兄弟",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "parent (cancelCtx/timerCtx)\n   ↓ (children 链表)\n   ├─ child1 (cancelCtx)\n   │     ↓\n   │     └─ grandchild1\n   └─ child2 (timerCtx)\n父取消 → 所有子、孙全部级联取消\n子取消 → 不影响父和兄弟",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vFkHfkm_KqwDrbjw2ejvA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -5667.238817713328,
      "y": 975.6031666283184,
      "width": 386.8798522949219,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bHl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 982008084,
      "version": 31,
      "versionNonce": 465963418,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479415,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为什么 WithCancel 必须 defer cancel？\n不调用 cancel 会：\n子 context 一直挂在父 children 里\ntimerCtx 的定时器不会停\n监听 <-ctx.Done() 的 goroutine 永远阻塞\n→ goroutine 泄漏、内存泄漏",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "为什么 WithCancel 必须 defer cancel？\n不调用 cancel 会：\n子 context 一直挂在父 children 里\ntimerCtx 的定时器不会停\n监听 <-ctx.Done() 的 goroutine 永远阻塞\n→ goroutine 泄漏、内存泄漏",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "s_sdf_MtoAXId2Zg3JBOW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -5666.949829008658,
      "y": 1157.211925463116,
      "width": 567.8599243164062,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bHm",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1205386260,
      "version": 57,
      "versionNonce": 876987994,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479415,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Context.Value 查找顺序是什么？\n从当前节点向上递归查找父链，直到找到 key 或到 emptyCtx。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Context.Value 查找顺序是什么？\n从当前节点向上递归查找父链，直到找到 key 或到 emptyCtx。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
