      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Hybrid 混合架构",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Hybrid 混合架构",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "edHS7fAxEvNjGAAbauPbY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4212.624743350501,
      "y": 6480.079027463054,
      "width": 764.2855224609375,
      "height": 40.02691926460283,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKb",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1794878947,
      "version": 607,
      "versionNonce": 777975258,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "混合架构结合了 SFU 和 MCU 的优点，根据不同的场景和参与者的条件，动态选择不同的媒体流处理方式。\n例如，在小规模会议中使用 P2P 或 SFU，而在大规模会议中使用 MCU 来集中控制视频流。",
      "fontSize": 16.010767705841133,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "混合架构结合了 SFU 和 MCU 的优点，根据不同的场景和参与者的条件，动态选择不同的媒体流处理方式。\n例如，在小规模会议中使用 P2P 或 SFU，而在大规模会议中使用 MCU 来集中控制视频流。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "e17sj552bVZsnfscIaMMa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3883.566457287214,
      "y": 6532.383329813765,
      "width": 448,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKc",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1873934723,
      "version": 597,
      "versionNonce": 360131226,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "更灵活，可以根据会议规模或参与者的网络条件动态调整架构。\n能够兼顾大规模和小规模场景的性能和带宽需求。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "更灵活，可以根据会议规模或参与者的网络条件动态调整架构。\n能够兼顾大规模和小规模场景的性能和带宽需求。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "38LTvrDylXDpOoOBn_YbG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3890.5946826809395,
      "y": 6700.878479143543,
      "width": 384,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKd",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 182309155,
      "version": 624,
      "versionNonce": 2099955546,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "复杂度较高，需要实现更复杂的调度和资源管理机制。\n可能会增加开发和运维的成本。\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "复杂度较高，需要实现更复杂的调度和资源管理机制。\n可能会增加开发和运维的成本。\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
