      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Edge Computing（边缘计算）架构",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Edge Computing（边缘计算）架构",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "dvbxc3bAmEX2z35R9_88e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3473.610036589242,
      "y": 4477.753975611469,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKs",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1431114627,
      "version": 154,
      "versionNonce": 1904326298,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "概述：在 Edge Computing 架构中，媒体流通过位于网络边缘的服务器（例如，CDN 节点、区域性数据中心）进\n行转发和处理，而不是依赖于中心化的服务器。边缘计算通过将计算和存储资源放置在离用户更近的地方，减少了\n延迟并提高了吞吐量。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "概述：在 Edge Computing 架构中，媒体流通过位于网络边缘的服务器（例如，CDN 节点、区域性数据中心）进行转发和处理，而不是依赖于中心化的服务器。边缘计算通过将计算和存储资源放置在离用户更近的地方，减少了延迟并提高了吞吐量。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aPwGy-uLKHONJIChul_OS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3097.610036589242,
      "y": 4567.753975611469,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 33925923,
      "version": 154,
      "versionNonce": 268686170,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "优点：",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "优点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ANBqvarHri_otptGnbC0k",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3377.610036589242,
      "y": 4597.753975611469,
      "width": 608,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKu",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 654986947,
      "version": 154,
      "versionNonce": 2040813594,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "通过将计算资源分散到地理位置更接近用户的地方，极大地减少了延迟，提高了性能。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "通过将计算资源分散到地理位置更接近用户的地方，极大地减少了延迟，提高了性能。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QqqFbH2pcTGj40DJu0MPd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3297.610036589242,
      "y": 4627.753975611469,
      "width": 448,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
