    },
    {
      "id": "kDGn8DgLM-fkbOnDeCk2E",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3337.610036589242,
      "y": 4687.753975611469,
      "width": 528,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 620855715,
      "version": 154,
      "versionNonce": 886724186,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "需要在多个地理位置部署边缘服务器，这会增加基础设施的复杂性和成本。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "需要在多个地理位置部署边缘服务器，这会增加基础设施的复杂性和成本。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SynsWr_OYqScXDt9A0lYH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3201.610036589242,
      "y": 4717.753975611469,
      "width": 256,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1497847107,
      "version": 154,
      "versionNonce": 1722972954,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "管理和协调边缘节点可能较为复杂。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "管理和协调边缘节点可能较为复杂。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HJSdBxoEAl7Jem2umXx2Q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3245.250366745075,
      "y": 4832.414474516527,
      "width": 392.97576904296875,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 416396515,
      "version": 135,
      "versionNonce": 463996890,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cloud-based Video Infrastructure (云视频基础设施)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cloud-based Video Infrastructure (云视频基础设施)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vpG_Lq2yR1lkrW0Anqc2k",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3443.380495437081,
      "y": 4865.812898998004,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 590291075,
      "version": 106,
      "versionNonce": 1540226202,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "概述：这种架构使用云基础设施来处理大规模视频通话和直播流。所有的信令、媒体流转发、编解码和处理都通过\n云服务器来实现。云服务提供商可以提供自动扩展、负载均衡和容错等功能，能够支持从小型会议到超大规模会议\n的所有场景。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "概述：这种架构使用云基础设施来处理大规模视频通话和直播流。所有的信令、媒体流转发、编解码和处理都通过云服务器来实现。云服务提供商可以提供自动扩展、负载均衡和容错等功能，能够支持从小型会议到超大规模会议的所有场景。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kJZXyYbCuuW3uOcaqIfBE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3067.380495437081,
      "y": 4955.812898998004,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
