      "versionNonce": 146463834,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "缺点：",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "缺点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AE9_bCOZuIcgRsX9PwJGD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3219.380495437081,
      "y": 5105.812898998004,
      "width": 352,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2071700035,
      "version": 106,
      "versionNonce": 949109018,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "成本可能较高，特别是当使用大量云计算资源时。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "成本可能较高，特别是当使用大量云计算资源时。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZH2GYElArW-i-Pj2hqvYY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3307.380495437081,
      "y": 5135.812898998004,
      "width": 528,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1760846307,
      "version": 106,
      "versionNonce": 1772031450,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "会受到网络带宽和云服务商数据中心的地理位置限制，可能存在延迟问题。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "会受到网络带宽和云服务商数据中心的地理位置限制，可能存在延迟问题。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CTXPVll8YuCA4LhslMvYh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3175.0941863787443,
      "y": 5203.200722338106,
      "width": 233.72620662429796,
      "height": 20.558573388669856,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 343158147,
      "version": 160,
      "versionNonce": 552878746,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Decentralized (去中心化) 架构",
      "fontSize": 16.446858710935885,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Decentralized (去中心化) 架构",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Brr-a-zcda_BwU_afq3rg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3446.0361511859332,
      "y": 5230.933210867313,
      "width": 787.3599853515625,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1094288675,
      "version": 139,
      "versionNonce": 1229250394,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "概述：去中心化架构是 WebRTC 的一个可能扩展，它使得所有参与者都能在一个去中心化的网络中进行实时通\n信，没有单一的控制服务器。在这种架构中，参与者直接互相通信，可能依赖于区块链或分布式哈希表（DHT）\n来管理信令和媒体流。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "概述：去中心化架构是 WebRTC 的一个可能扩展，它使得所有参与者都能在一个去中心化的网络中进行实时通信，没有单一的控制服务器。在这种架构中，参与者直接互相通信，可能依赖于区块链或分布式哈希表（DHT）来管理信令和媒体流。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "sFeqm6rroICf_WywdPrFw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3076.356158510152,
      "y": 5320.933210867313,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1186130115,
      "version": 139,
      "versionNonce": 2128864282,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479419,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "优点：",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "优点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qJ6PCtso7Vb2HVHHRPMQC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3276.356158510152,
      "y": 5350.933210867313,
      "width": 448,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
