      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "技术实现复杂，尚处于实验阶段，尚未大规模应用。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "技术实现复杂，尚处于实验阶段，尚未大规模应用。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4VabyxRV4xYCKH-uJFVjl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3236.356158510152,
      "y": 5470.933210867313,
      "width": 368,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLF",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 433721059,
      "version": 139,
      "versionNonce": 732959706,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "在带宽管理、流量控制和用户管理上可能遇到挑战。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "在带宽管理、流量控制和用户管理上可能遇到挑战。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rhDOtfw_lcQmAUiyipJbE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3348.356158510152,
      "y": 5500.933210867313,
      "width": 592,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1444690563,
      "version": 139,
      "versionNonce": 1190430874,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "去中心化架构的实现可能在性能和扩展性上存在限制，尤其是在大规模多人会议中。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "去中心化架构的实现可能在性能和扩展性上存在限制，尤其是在大规模多人会议中。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "lCnrEyKkIOPyc0axaxge4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3150.252832718064,
      "y": 5591.7437556485875,
      "width": 250.6238250732422,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLH",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 207090211,
      "version": 86,
      "versionNonce": 323773786,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Layered Video Coding (LVC) 架构",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Layered Video Coding (LVC) 架构",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "_158vxfNZTb2DYlk0sNOE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3423.6161437344276,
      "y": 5627.376067817557,
      "width": 798.43212890625,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1568388547,
      "version": 51,
      "versionNonce": 1779083802,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "概述：LVC（分层视频编码）架构通过在视频流中使用多层次的编码技术，将视频流分成不同质量的层级。每个参\n与者可以根据自己的带宽状况，动态地选择不同质量的视频层。LVC 可以结合 SFU 或 MCU 使用，以便在带宽有\n限的情况下优化视频流传输。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "概述：LVC（分层视频编码）架构通过在视频流中使用多层次的编码技术，将视频流分成不同质量的层级。每个参与者可以根据自己的带宽状况，动态地选择不同质量的视频层。LVC 可以结合 SFU 或 MCU 使用，以便在带宽有限的情况下优化视频流传输。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uW9AwYlMR9eyYlVoqbj2Q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3048.4000792813026,
      "y": 5717.376067817557,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1218839907,
      "version": 51,
      "versionNonce": 35804890,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "优点：",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "优点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "j1wgVCgosBkNSItIIrYmq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3304.4000792813026,
      "y": 5747.376067817557,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1696948483,
      "version": 51,
      "versionNonce": 1009150874,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "可以根据每个参与者的网络条件进行灵活的质量控制，减少不必要的带宽消耗。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "可以根据每个参与者的网络条件进行灵活的质量控制，减少不必要的带宽消耗。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "oFUmjks4FcNTdts31q7k9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3232.4000792813026,
      "y": 5777.376067817557,
      "width": 416,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLL",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1551386787,
      "version": 51,
      "versionNonce": 1850337370,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "提高了视频通信的适应性，能够满足不同网络环境的需求。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "提高了视频通信的适应性，能够满足不同网络环境的需求。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "N7eCQ81LuWQ58wFHOVv-u",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3048.4000792813026,
      "y": 5807.376067817557,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
