      "updated": 1776677479421,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. relay（中继候选者）\n格式：`udp4 relay\n203.0.113.1:54321`\n说明：通过 TURN 服务器中继的\n地址\n优先级：最低（作为最后备选，需\n要额外带宽成本）",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "To5mQWRNHPPXJmjtCQVn_",
      "originalText": "3. relay（中继候选者）\n格式：`udp4 relay 203.0.113.1:54321`\n说明：通过 TURN 服务器中继的地址\n优先级：最低（作为最后备选，需要额外带宽成本）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
