      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776754581136,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "无法处理正常连接",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "无法处理正常连接",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OTvcPpL8jJDWNNyKTbpxl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7589.006511371864,
      "y": 5034.123181832717,
      "width": 597.2396240234375,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bST",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1954625475,
      "version": 183,
      "versionNonce": 1471646142,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776754581136,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "防护方案:\n1. SYN Cookie\n服务器不保存半连接状态\n而是把状态编码在SYN-ACK的seq号中\n客户端回复ACK时，服务器从seq号恢复状态\n\n2. 增加半连接队列\n# 增加SYN队列大小\nnet.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog = 4096\n\n3. 减少SYN超时时间\n# 减少半连接保留时间\nnet.ipv4.tcp_synack_retries = 2\n\n4. 使用防火墙/负载均衡\n# 限制单IP的SYN数量\niptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn -m limit --limit 1/s -j ACCEPT\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "防护方案:\n1. SYN Cookie\n服务器不保存半连接状态\n而是把状态编码在SYN-ACK的seq号中\n客户端回复ACK时，服务器从seq号恢复状态\n\n2. 增加半连接队列\n# 增加SYN队列大小\nnet.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog = 4096\n\n3. 减少SYN超时时间\n# 减少半连接保留时间\nnet.ipv4.tcp_synack_retries = 2\n\n4. 使用防火墙/负载均衡\n# 限制单IP的SYN数量\niptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn -m limit --limit 1/s -j ACCEPT\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
