      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "SYN \n(seq=100)\n随机初始序列号",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Ai6Z1hqRLIrV1-Scmy8vs",
      "originalText": "SYN \n(seq=100)\n随机初始序列号",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "_RCVhJ_fHTi88x6ImUN73",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5099.688078001505,
      "y": 7139.456935398126,
      "width": 295.1999816894531,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bTE",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 923746851,
      "version": 267,
      "versionNonce": 122133566,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776754581137,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "启动计时器\n\n动态计算 RTO（重传超时时间）\n\n基于RTT（往返时间）：\nRTO = RTT + 4 × RTTVAR\n\n例子：\nRTT = 100ms（往返时间）\nRTTVAR = 10ms（RTT变化）\nRTO = 100 + 4×10 = 140ms",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "启动计时器\n\n动态计算 RTO（重传超时时间）\n\n基于RTT（往返时间）：\nRTO = RTT + 4 × RTTVAR\n\n例子：\nRTT = 100ms（往返时间）\nRTTVAR = 10ms（RTT变化）\nRTO = 100 + 4×10 = 140ms",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
