      "updated": 1776677479432,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "OIDC架构\nRelying Party RP 依赖方（业务应用）\nOP 授权认证服务器（IDP）\nEnd User 用户\nID Token（身份令牌）、Access Token（资源令牌）、Refresh Token",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "OIDC架构\nRelying Party RP 依赖方（业务应用）\nOP 授权认证服务器（IDP）\nEnd User 用户\nID Token（身份令牌）、Access Token（资源令牌）、Refresh Token",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aLL-rzeg5DGfBM4QEVatC",
      "type": "image",
      "x": -11903.514631264086,
