    {
      "id": "3DoSb8gUroJwkZJewT3a_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -12126.328315747442,
      "y": 3034.6358848493032,
      "width": 616.68798828125,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bWK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1442195301,
      "version": 74,
      "versionNonce": 416671258,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776677479432,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CSRF 跨站请求伪造\n利用浏览器会自动带上当前域名 Cookie的特性，用户已登录正常网站，访问恶意网站，\n恶意网站悄悄发起请求，冒充用户操作（改密码、转账、下单）\nCSRF 拿不到 Cookie，只是借 Cookie 发请求\n\n防护措施\n接口携带一次性 CSRF Token\nCookie：SameSite=Strict\n后端校验 Origin/Referer 请求来源",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CSRF 跨站请求伪造\n利用浏览器会自动带上当前域名 Cookie的特性，用户已登录正常网站，访问恶意网站，\n恶意网站悄悄发起请求，冒充用户操作（改密码、转账、下单）\nCSRF 拿不到 Cookie，只是借 Cookie 发请求\n\n防护措施\n接口携带一次性 CSRF Token\nCookie：SameSite=Strict\n后端校验 Origin/Referer 请求来源",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WSpAEioAAoTYiYuTTzA2d",
