    {
      "id": "yqXLKWw95Ri4IoHKyDG1Q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4900.261970461701,
      "y": 3524.562019928361,
      "width": 1221.6397705078125,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bXJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 866940615,
      "version": 313,
      "versionNonce": 1160619234,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776754563316,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TLS交互流程\n\n四次握手\nHTTPS 使用的加密协议从最初的 SSL（Secure Sockets Layer）演变为 TLS（Transport Layer Security）。\n\n目前广泛使用的是 TLS 1.2 和 TLS 1.3。TLS 1.3 引入了更快的握手机制（0-RTT），进一步降低了延迟（QUIC内嵌使用这个协议）。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TLS交互流程\n\n四次握手\nHTTPS 使用的加密协议从最初的 SSL（Secure Sockets Layer）演变为 TLS（Transport Layer Security）。\n\n目前广泛使用的是 TLS 1.2 和 TLS 1.3。TLS 1.3 引入了更快的握手机制（0-RTT），进一步降低了延迟（QUIC内嵌使用这个协议）。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TkfTCgqCP7Yy5mucYWFR5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6232.142842984152,
      "y": 3482.6119960458127,
      "width": 386.7039489746094,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bXK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1280396201,
      "version": 117,
      "versionNonce": 866826402,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776754563316,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HTTP 握手升级协议 → 变成长连接 TCP 双向帧通道\n一次握手，永久双向收发，不用反复三次握手",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HTTP 握手升级协议 → 变成长连接 TCP 双向帧通道\n一次握手，永久双向收发，不用反复三次握手",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wb_QIc5hAiSduWB4HPvAC",
      "type": "image",
      "x": 6230.702473760991,
      "y": 3552.027281770306,
      "width": 740.6907129612893,
      "height": 1024.5865770069709,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bXL",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 783496903,
      "version": 266,
      "versionNonce": 1721254909,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777887718194,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "status": "error",
      "fileId": "da5d157b445f3b36b120a47b4cd43fa715d6cf95",
      "scale": [
        1,
        1
      ],
      "crop": null
    },
    {
      "id": "rt9uLC2f9ZcEt5HAhFhBy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7045.205687624132,
      "y": 3687.3400757107693,
      "width": 421.8558654785156,
      "height": 320,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bXM",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1751936519,
      "version": 135,
      "versionNonce": 1047164962,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776754563316,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 先 TCP 三次握手\n2. 再 HTTP 升级握手（101）\n3. 握手完 → HTTP 彻底结束\n4. 之后完全走 WebSocket 帧协议\n5. 双向全双工：谁都能随时发消息，不需要等对方请求\n6. 心跳 Ping/Pong 是 WebSocket 原生自带\n7. 关闭走 WebSocket Close 帧\n8. 最后 TCP 四次挥手\n\n\n\nWebSocket 之所以能双向，不是因为魔法，是因为：\nTCP 本身就是全双工的\nHTTP 是 “请求 - 响应” 半双工\nWebSocket 只是脱掉 HTTP 外壳，直接用 TCP 双向通道\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. 先 TCP 三次握手\n2. 再 HTTP 升级握手（101）\n3. 握手完 → HTTP 彻底结束\n4. 之后完全走 WebSocket 帧协议\n5. 双向全双工：谁都能随时发消息，不需要等对方请求\n6. 心跳 Ping/Pong 是 WebSocket 原生自带\n7. 关闭走 WebSocket Close 帧\n8. 最后 TCP 四次挥手\n\n\n\nWebSocket 之所以能双向，不是因为魔法，是因为：\nTCP 本身就是全双工的\nHTTP 是 “请求 - 响应” 半双工\nWebSocket 只是脱掉 HTTP 外壳，直接用 TCP 双向通道\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QjfyERg57aPo9iZjhx6g6",
      "type": "image",
      "x": 7765.056753472211,
      "y": 3544.2985984044362,
      "width": 460.2128535795029,
      "height": 1043.6322978810774,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bXN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1110181191,
      "version": 249,
      "versionNonce": 553371219,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
